name: 🐇 a bunny floating in precision (frame 395)
description:
Still from A Bunny Floating in Precision. Part of a series of studies which confront the compromise between precision and representation as experienced in digital systems which use floating point number formats.

This edition used the Stanford Bunny Model, source: Stanford University Computer Graphics Laboratory
